      "title": "Conflict in Sudan’s Breadbasket Threatens Food Supplies Nationwide",
      "rawText": "Conflict in Sudan’s Breadbasket Threatens Food Supplies Nationwide tfinstuen@fews.net Sun, 04/05/2026 - 14:06 February 13, 2024 Sudan East Africa Conflict Integrated Food Security Analysis Food Security Humanitarian Hannah Button FEWS NET Senior Communications Lead",
